#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwrite; is a text editor by &kde; allowing you to edit one file at the time "
"per window."
msgstr ""
"&kwrite; estas tekstredaktilo de &kde; permesante al vi redakti unu dosieron "
"samtempe per fenestro."

#. Tag: keyword
